                    <p>
                        After analysis, the application does presents its findings in relation to the quality of the document as it was subjected to comparison with its compliance to the Philippine Laws as stated in the constitution and the general recommendation whether to accept the terms, be wary of possible unfair agreements and reject the terms if the results would return unfavorable values.
                    </p>
